Aboitiz Power of Philippines Rises to 3-Week High on Power Plant Takeover

-- B y   I a n   S a y s o n
-- 
2011-04-01T02:39:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/aboitiz-power-of-philippines-rises-to-3-week-high-on-power-plant-takeover.html
Aboitiz Power Corp. (AP)  advanced to the
highest in three weeks in  Manila  after the company said a unit
agreed to buy out its partner in a hydro-power plant in a
transaction valued at $30 million.  Aboitiz Power climbed 1.7 percent to 30.50 pesos as of
10:34 a.m. local time, bound for the highest close since March
11. The benchmark Philippine Stock Exchange Index increased 0.8
percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ian Sayson in Manila at 
 isayson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Darren Boey at 
 dboey@bloomberg.net  